2026-03-30T05:35:38.255Z JOY-0016 comment.added "ADR-024: Source changes from .joy/ai/capabilities/*.md to data/capabilities/*.md + data/ai/agents/*.yaml (embedded). Applies to conceive, design, test, document. Output is generated per tool into respective tool directories." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
2026-03-30T05:35:43.339Z JOY-0018 comment.added "ADR-024: Agent source is now data/ai/agents/*.yaml + templates/ai/tools/claude-code/agents/*.md. Output goes to .claude/agents/*.md. No intermediate .joy/ files." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
