2026-03-30T05:35:54.340Z JOY-0029 comment.added "ADR-024 introduces data/process/ as structured YAML source for status flow, transitions, and gates. This data feeds into the AI generation pipeline (workflow.md, agent files). When implementing process model items, the YAML structures in data/process/ should be designed to serve both joy-core runtime logic and template rendering." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
