2026-03-30T06:10:12.799Z JOY-0091 comment.added "Plan: Implement ADR-024 data/templates split in 10 steps. (1) Create data/process/workflow.yaml with all statuses, transitions, gates. (2) Create data/ai/agents/*.yaml for 7 work capabilities. (3) Move templates from data/ai/ to templates/ai/, doc scaffolds to templates/docs/. (4) Enhance instructions.md and SKILL.md with MiniJinja workflow blocks. (5) Create tool-specific agent frame templates. (6) Build joy-core ai_templates.rs rendering engine. (7) Rewrite ai.rs to use new rendering pipeline. (8) Update init.rs gitignore entries. (9) Add legacy .joy/ai/ cleanup. (10) Tests." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
